# BatteryData âš¡ï¸

A lightweight macOS menu bar app that shows detailed battery information, power usage, and history charts.

---

## âœ¨ Features

- Menu bar app with a clean and minimal UI
- Battery percentage, charging state, and AC status
- Real-time power usage (W)
- Time to empty / time to full estimation
- Battery health, cycle count, temperature
- Power adapter type and wattage
- Battery usage history charts
- Optional expanded battery info in the status bar
- Launch at login support
- macOS notifications:
  - Low battery alerts (20%, 10%, 5%)
  - Fully charged notification
  - Power spike detection

---

## ğŸ§­ Status Bar Modes

BatteryData supports a simple status bar behavior:

- **Expanded battery info â€” OFF (default)**
  Shows only the battery icon in the menu bar.

- **Expanded battery info â€” ON**
  Shows battery percentage, ETA, and power usage directly in the menu bar.

This can be toggled in **Settings â†’ Status Bar**.

---

## ğŸ“Š Charts

The app displays battery history charts:
- Battery percentage over time
- Power usage (W) over time

Charts are shown inside a popover window and update automatically.

---

